WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-US

00:00:04.220 --> 00:00:10.420
In this tutorial we are going to make little round leaf with picot and spiral leafstalk.

00:00:14.180 --> 00:00:27.300
Make a chain of 8

00:00:27.300 --> 00:00:33.500
and join the chain in a round with a slip stitch.

00:00:33.500 --> 00:00:34.900
Round 1

00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:37.460
make 1 chain stitch up

00:00:37.460 --> 00:00:48.700
Now work in the round. Single crochet 2,

00:00:48.700 --> 00:01:21.700
make 2 half double crochet stitches and on top of each make a 3-chain picot (chain 3 and slip stitch under 2 loops of half double crochet)

00:01:21.700 --> 00:01:42.820
2 double crochet and make a 3-chain picot on top of each post.

00:01:42.820 --> 00:02:16.020
2 treble crochet (yarn over hook 2 times for a treble stitch) and make a picot on top of each treble

00:02:16.020 --> 00:02:56.780
2 double treble crochet (yarn over hook 3 times for a double treble stitch) and on top of each post make a 3-chain picot.

00:02:56.780 --> 00:02:57.740
Now repeat

00:02:57.740 --> 00:03:22.540
make 2 treble crochet stitches with picot

00:03:22.540 --> 00:03:45.140
2 double crochet with picot

00:03:45.140 --> 00:04:15.620
2 half double crochet with picot

00:04:15.620 --> 00:04:23.340
single crochet 2 in a round.

00:04:23.340 --> 00:04:31.340
To finish the round make a slip stitch through the first chain stitch.

00:04:35.140 --> 00:04:37.940
Our little leaf is ready!

00:04:43.780 --> 00:04:45.700
Let`s make a spiral leafstalk.

00:04:49.620 --> 00:05:07.380
chain 10 (9 chain stitches for the leafstalk and 1 chain stitch up)

00:05:07.380 --> 00:05:23.420
Into the second stitch from the hook make 2 single crochet.

00:05:23.420 --> 00:05:33.100
into the next chain work 2 single crochet stitches.

00:05:33.100 --> 00:06:13.820
And continue, make 2 single crochet stitches in each of next chain stitches of our leafstalk.

00:06:13.820 --> 00:06:17.860
We`ve reached the last stitch, make 2 single crochet through the last chain stitch.

00:06:17.860 --> 00:06:28.300
To finish the work, make a slip stitch through the first chain stitch on the round.

00:06:31.500 --> 00:06:36.620
Leaf is ready now! You can cut the yarn.

00:06:43.500 --> 00:06:48.340
In this tutorial we`ve learned how to make these beautiful leaves.

